3. Small functions and doing only one thing can help you understand functions faster, and when you first understand the function's function, you will remember it when you encounter it again, thereby improving the efficiency and effectiveness of understanding and increasing comprehensibility.

education: University courses only
warmup-p2-q1:
There are three functions in class “WarmUp”.
main function: judge the length of numbers, if it less or equal than 0, the result is null, if not, call the sumNumbers method to count the numbers in the array that are less than or equal to 10.0.
sunNumbers function: sum initial value is 0, traverse the number in the array, as long as it is greater than 10, the sum will be increased by one.
countNumbers: count initial value is 0, traverse the number in the array, as long as it is greater than 10, the count will be increased by one.
code_explanation: Used to verify the validity of a given date (including year, month, day) and calculate the total number of days from the start date (January 1, 1900). It returns the number of days from the start date for valid dates and an error message for invalid dates by checking for leap year rules, number of days in the month, etc.
